sequenceDiagram
    participant U as You
    participant R as run_all.py
    participant D as make_cohort
    participant E as experiment.run()
    participant S as Simulator (Qiskit/PennyLane)
    participant A as quantum_analyst
    U->>R: python run_all.py
    R->>D: generate cohort
    D-->>R: cohort.csv
    loop each of 3 experiments
        R->>E: run(quick=False)
        E->>S: run circuits (quantum) + fit classical
        S-->>E: measurements / scores
        E-->>R: results/expN.json
    end
    R->>A: read results
    A-->>R: verdict_cards.json
    R-->>U: charts + verdicts
